Write a program which counts the frequency of a words in a corpus of text as well as the sentence
numbers in which they appear, outputted sorted by most frequently occurring.

Example:

Input:

Meet Jon. Jon is a computer programmer and lives in Connecticut. Jon is tall.

Output:

jon, 3, [1, 2, 3]

is, 2, [2, 3]

meet, 1, [1]

a, 1, [2]

computer, 1, [2]

...

You can write in any language of your choosing. Your code should be runnable. Please provide an
example of how to execute it (e.g., ./word_count.py input.txt)